@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam participantBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam actorBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam actorBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam boundaryBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam boundaryBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam controlBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam controlBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam entityBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam entityBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam databaseBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam databaseBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Khach hang\n(Customer)" as Customer #Yellow
actor "Admin/Staff" as Staff #Yellow
boundary "ContactPage\n(Public Form)" as PubUI #Yellow
boundary "ContactManagePage\n(Admin Panel)" as AdmUI #Yellow
boundary "AuthGuard\n(Staff/Admin)" as AuthGuard #Yellow
boundary "contactService\n(API Client)" as APIClient #Yellow
boundary "api.ts\n(Axios)" as Axios #Yellow
control "JwtMiddleware" as JWT #Yellow
control "ContactController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "ContactService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "UnitOfWork" as UoW #Yellow
database "GenericRepository\nContactMessage" as Repo #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL\n(PMC_Tour)" as DB #Yellow

== 1: Khach hang gui lien he (POST /api/Contact - Public) ==

Customer -> PubUI : 1: Mo trang Contact (/contact)
activate PubUI

PubUI -> PubUI : 1.1: Render form contact (Navbar, Hero,\nform fields, contact info, map)
PubUI --> Customer : 1.1.1: Hien thi form: Name, Email, Subject, Message

Customer -> PubUI : 1.2: Dien form va nhan "Send Message"
activate PubUI

PubUI -> PubUI : 1.2.1: Validate frontend (required fields)
alt [1.2.2] Thieu thong tin
    PubUI --> Customer : 1.2.2.1: Bao loi validate
else [1.2.3] Hop le
    PubUI -> APIClient : 1.2.3.1: contactService.create(formData)
    activate APIClient

    APIClient -> Axios : 1.2.3.2: api.post('/Contact', { name, email, subject, message })
    activate Axios
    note right: Khong can token -\nday la endpoint public
    Axios -> Ctrl : 1.2.3.3: HTTP POST /api/Contact
    activate Ctrl

    Ctrl -> Svc : 1.2.3.4: CreateAsync(createContactRequest)
    activate Svc

    Svc -> Svc : 1.2.3.4.1: AutoMapper.Map<CreateContactRequest -> ContactMessage>
    Svc -> Svc : 1.2.3.4.2: Set CreatedAt = UtcNow

    Svc -> UoW : 1.2.3.4.3: ContactMessages.AddAsync(contact)
    activate UoW
    UoW -> Repo : 1.2.3.4.3.1: AddAsync(ContactMessage)
    activate Repo
    Repo -> DB : 1.2.3.4.3.2: INSERT INTO ContactMessages\n(Name, Email, Subject, Message,\nIsRead=false, CreatedAt)
    activate DB
    DB --> Repo : 1.2.3.4.3.3: Created
    deactivate DB
    deactivate Repo
    deactivate UoW

    Svc -> UoW : 1.2.3.5: SaveChangesAsync()
    activate UoW
    UoW -> DB : 1.2.3.5.1: COMMIT
    activate DB
    DB --> UoW : 1.2.3.5.2: success
    deactivate DB
    deactivate UoW

    Svc --> Ctrl : 1.2.3.6: ApiResponse.Ok("Message sent successfully")
    deactivate Svc

    Ctrl --> Axios : 1.2.3.7: HTTP 200 + JSON
    deactivate Ctrl

    Axios --> APIClient : 1.2.3.8: res.data
    deactivate Axios

    APIClient --> PubUI : 1.2.3.9: ApiResponse
    deactivate APIClient

    PubUI -> PubUI : 1.2.3.10: Set submitSuccess=true, show "Message Sent!"
    PubUI -> PubUI : 1.2.3.11: Reset form ve trang thai ban dau
    PubUI --> Customer : 1.2.3.12: Hien thi thong bao thanh cong

    note right: Sau 3 giay tu dong reset\ntrang thai submitSuccess

end
deactivate PubUI

== 2: Admin xem danh sach lien he (GET /api/Contact - [Authorize]) ==

Staff -> AdmUI : 2: Mo trang Contact Manage (/contact/manage)
activate AdmUI

AdmUI -> AuthGuard : 2.1: Kiem tra authentication & roles (STAFF hoac ADMIN)
activate AuthGuard
alt [2.1.1] Khong co quyen
    AuthGuard --> AdmUI : 2.1.1.1: Redirect
else [2.1.2] Co quyen
    AuthGuard --> AdmUI : 2.1.2.1: Render
end
deactivate AuthGuard

AdmUI -> APIClient : 2.2: contactService.getAll()
activate APIClient

APIClient -> Axios : 2.2.1: api.get('/Contact')
activate Axios

Axios -> JWT : 2.2.2: HTTP GET /api/Contact + Bearer token
activate JWT

JWT -> JWT : 2.2.2.1: Validate JWT
alt [2.2.2.2] Token hop le
    JWT -> JWT : 2.2.2.2.1: Attach User
else [2.2.2.3] Token khong hop le
    note right: [Authorize] -> 401
end
JWT -> Ctrl : 2.2.2.4: Chuyen tiep request
deactivate JWT

activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc : 2.2.3: GetAllAsync(pagedRequest)
activate Svc

Svc -> UoW : 2.2.3.1: ContactMessages.GetQueryable()
activate UoW
UoW -> Repo : 2.2.3.1.1: IQueryable<ContactMessage>
deactivate UoW

Repo -> Repo : 2.2.3.2: Loc SearchTerm (Name, Email, Subject)
Repo -> Repo : 2.2.3.3: WHERE IsDeleted = false
Repo -> Repo : 2.2.3.4: CountAsync()

Repo -> DB : 2.2.3.5: SELECT ... FROM ContactMessages\nWHERE IsDeleted=false\nORDER BY CreatedAt DESC\nOFFSET ... LIMIT ...
activate DB
DB --> Repo : 2.2.3.5.1: List<ContactMessage>
deactivate DB

Repo --> Svc : 2.2.3.6: List<ContactMessage>
Svc -> Svc : 2.2.3.7: AutoMapper.Map -> List<ContactResponse>
Svc --> Ctrl : 2.2.3.8: ApiResponse<PagedResult<ContactResponse>>
deactivate Svc

Ctrl --> Axios : 2.2.4: HTTP 200 + JSON
deactivate Ctrl

Axios --> APIClient : 2.2.5: res.data
deactivate Axios

APIClient --> AdmUI : 2.2.6: ApiResponse (items: ContactItem[])
deactivate APIClient

AdmUI -> AdmUI : 2.2.7: Filter client-side theo searchTerm
AdmUI --> Staff : 2.2.8: Hien thi bang: ID, Name, Subject, Date, Status (New/Read)
deactivate AdmUI

== 3: Admin xem chi tiet tin nhan (Client-side) ==

Staff -> AdmUI : 3: Click "View" tren mot tin nhan
activate AdmUI

AdmUI -> AdmUI : 3.1: setSelectedContact(contact)
AdmUI --> Staff : 3.2: Mo Modal chi tiet
note right: Modal hien thi:\n- Name, Email\n- Subject, Message\n- Sent At\n- Status (New/Read)\n\nKhong co API call rieng -\ndata da co tu getAll()
deactivate AdmUI

== 4: Admin xoa tin nhan (DELETE /api/Contact/{id} - [Authorize]) ==

Staff -> AdmUI : 4: Click "Delete" -> Confirm
activate AdmUI

AdmUI -> AdmUI : 4.1: confirm('Delete this message?')
alt [4.1.1] Huy bo
    note right: Khong thuc hien xoa
else [4.1.2] Xac nhan
    AdmUI -> APIClient : 4.1.2.1: contactService.delete(id)
    activate APIClient

    APIClient -> Axios : 4.1.2.2: api.delete('/Contact/{id}')
    activate Axios

    Axios -> JWT : 4.1.2.3: HTTP DELETE + Bearer
    activate JWT
    JWT -> Ctrl : 4.1.2.3.1: Validate token
    deactivate JWT

    activate Ctrl
    Ctrl -> Svc : 4.1.2.4: DeleteAsync(id)
    activate Svc

    Svc -> UoW : 4.1.2.4.1: ContactMessages.GetByIdAsync(id)
    activate UoW
    UoW -> DB : 4.1.2.4.1.1: SELECT ... WHERE Id = {id}
    activate DB
    DB --> UoW : 4.1.2.4.1.2: ContactMessage
    deactivate DB

    alt [4.1.2.4.2] Khong tim thay
        Svc --> Ctrl : 4.1.2.4.2.1: ApiResponse.Fail("Message not found", 404)
    else [4.1.2.4.3] Tim thay
        Svc -> Svc : 4.1.2.4.3.1: contact.IsDeleted = true (soft delete)
        UoW -> DB : 4.1.2.4.3.2: UPDATE ContactMessages SET\nIsDeleted=true, DeletedAt=UtcNow\nWHERE Id = {id}
        activate DB
        DB --> UoW : 4.1.2.4.3.3: updated
        deactivate DB
        deactivate UoW

        Svc -> UoW : 4.1.2.4.4: SaveChangesAsync()
        activate UoW
        UoW -> DB : 4.1.2.4.4.1: COMMIT
        activate DB
        DB --> UoW : 4.1.2.4.4.2: success
        deactivate DB
        deactivate UoW

        Svc --> Ctrl : 4.1.2.4.5: ApiResponse.Ok(true, "Message deleted")
    end
    deactivate Svc

    Ctrl --> Axios : 4.1.2.5: HTTP 200
    deactivate Ctrl

    Axios --> APIClient : 4.1.2.6: res.data
    deactivate Axios

    APIClient --> AdmUI : 4.1.2.7: ApiResponse
    deactivate APIClient

    AdmUI -> AdmUI : 4.1.2.8: invalidateQueries(['contactMessages'])
    AdmUI --> Staff : 4.1.2.9: Cap nhat bang (xoa dong)
end
deactivate AdmUI

@enduml
